@node "Requirements" "Requirements"
@{b} SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:@{ub}

  - Kickstart v3.0 or better
  - @{"MUI" link "Muinfo" 0} (Magic User Interface) v3.2 or better [available on Aminet]
     + Betterstring.mcc v11.3 or better [available on Aminet]
     + PopplaceHolder.mcc v15.2 of better [available on Aminet]
     + TransferAnim.mcc  v1.5 or better [available on Aminet]
        + Imagepool.library v37.0 or better [available on Aminet]
  - Scalos v1.2a or better

@{b} ADDITIONALLY SUPPORTS:@{ub}

  - OpenURL.library by Troels Hansen (troels@stud.cs.uit.no) [available on Aminet]

@endnode


